# Component Patterns & Examples

## 🎯 Component Architecture Patterns

### **Container Component Pattern:**
Reference: [src/components/containers/CalendarContainer.tsx](mdc:src/components/containers/CalendarContainer.tsx)

```typescript
// ✅ CORRECT - Container with styled props
import { StyledCalendarContainer } from '../../styles/Containers.style';

type CalendarContainerProps = {
  $calendarBackgroundColor?: string;
  children: React.ReactNode;
};

const CalendarContainer: React.FC<CalendarContainerProps> = ({
  $calendarBackgroundColor,
  children
}) => {
  return (
    <StyledCalendarContainer $calendarBackgroundColor={$calendarBackgroundColor}>
      {children}
    </StyledCalendarContainer>
